name: Rima
full_prompt: A girl named Rima goes to School, feeling happy
story_text: Scene 1: It's morning and Timmy is getting dressed for school. He puts on his favorite t-shirt and blue jeans.
Scene 2: Timmy eats breakfast before leaving for school. He has cereal with milk and fruit.
Scene 3: Timmy walks to school with his best friend Sarah. They hold hands and talk about their weekend plans.
Scene 4: Timmy's teacher Mrs. Johnson gives him a hug before class starts. She is wearing a red sweater and has a big smile on her face.
